  "texts": [
    "These checks are used to infer Pauli-X-and Pauli-Z-type stabilizer operators.",
    "The Pauli-X-type stabilizer operators are the product of Pauli-X terms on all of the qubits on two adjacent rows (Extended Data Fig. 4, left).",
    "The Pauli-Z stabilizer operators are the same as those of the surface code (Extended Data Fig. 3).",
    "We also show the support of logical Pauli-X and Pauli-Z stabilizer operators in Extended Data Fig. 4 (left) in green and blue, respectively.",
    "Once again, this stabilizer group can be regarded as S fin with respect to the simplified code-deformation theory we have presented."
